rComments: Overall great proff! Although the material is dry, professor explains concepts extremely clearly and is dedicated to his students doing well in class. Do the readings, go to class and ask questions. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!

Really good prof. Lectures are to the point and he clarifies and explains conceptsthemes very well. Structure of this class was a proposal, essay and final. He also is really helpful during office hours too. It's not a SUPER easy class, but do the readings and read his slides, and you'll do well. Recommended. He's great. You will learn too!

My favourite prof this semester. He speaks clearly, and frequently tells little jokes. His powerpoint slides are useful. He tells you exactly what he expects for the assignments and final exam. He engages with the class, and is very approachable. Overall, this is the kind of prof that you would want to take a class with.
He's easy going , his assignments aren't too hard , lectures are specific and clear and help a lot , he likes when students participate and he's also very helpful and kind.
